<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>prometheus on 대충어쩌고저쩌고샬라샬라</title><link>https://dntco43u.github.io/tags/prometheus/</link><description>Recent content in prometheus on 대충어쩌고저쩌고샬라샬라</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 15 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://dntco43u.github.io/tags/prometheus/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>prometheus</title><link>https://dntco43u.github.io/apps/prometheus/</link><pubDate>Mon, 15 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dntco43u.github.io/apps/prometheus/</guid><description>&lt;div class="alert alert-primary" role="alert"&gt;&lt;div class="h4 alert-heading" role="heading"&gt;작성 중&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id="docker-composeyml"&gt;docker-compose.yml&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#docker-composeyml" aria-label="Heading self-link"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d8dee9;background-color:#2e3440;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;vi /opt/prometheus/docker-compose.yml
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d8dee9;background-color:#2e3440;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yml" data-lang="yml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;services&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;prometheus&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;image&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; prom/prometheus:latest
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;container_name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; prometheus
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;networks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; - dev
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;ports&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; - &lt;span style="color:#b48ead"&gt;9090&lt;/span&gt;/tcp
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;user&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#b48ead"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#b48ead"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;volumes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; - /opt/prometheus/config:/etc/prometheus:rw
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; - /opt/prometheus/data:/prometheus:rw
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;command&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; - --config.file=/etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; - --web.config.file=/etc/prometheus/web.yml
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; - --storage.tsdb.path=/prometheus
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; - --storage.tsdb.retention.time=7d
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;restart&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; unless-stopped
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;networks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;dev&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;external&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1;font-weight:bold"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="proxy-구성"&gt;proxy 구성&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#proxy-%ea%b5%ac%ec%84%b1" aria-label="Heading self-link"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 id="proxy-구성-1"&gt;proxy 구성&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#proxy-%ea%b5%ac%ec%84%b1-1" aria-label="Heading self-link"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d8dee9;background-color:#2e3440;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;vi /opt/nginx/config/sites-available/loki.conf
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;...
 location / {
 include /etc/nginx/conf.d/include/proxy.conf;
 proxy_pass http://loki:3100;
 auth_basic &amp;#34;Authorization required&amp;#34;;
 auth_basic_user_file /etc/nginx/access/loki;
 proxy_intercept_errors on;
 allow 192.168.0.0/16;
 allow 2**.**.**.*; #sj9n7air
 allow 1**.***.**.*; #ec4mrjp5
 allow 1**.***.**.**; #m7jrgve9
 allow 1**.***.**.**; #gvp6nx1a
 allow 3*.***.***.***; #agknwpt3
 deny all;
 }
...
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>